## 13.3 Category-safety compile failures

Compile-fail documentation must demonstrate at least:

### Structural category mismatch

```rust
use mossignal::key::{ConnectionKey, NodeKey};

fn accepts_node(_: NodeKey) {}

accepts_node(ConnectionKey::from_u128(1));
```

### Signal-kind mismatch

```rust
